<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset Successful - JourNiva</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 540px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888888;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .brand {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4a90e2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>

        <p>
            This is a confirmation that your password has been successfully changed on <span class="brand">JourNiva</span>.
        </p>

        <p>
            If you did not perform this action, please contact us immediately.
        </p>

        <p>
            We're here to keep your account secure.
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
            <span class="brand">Team JourNiva</span> 
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
